Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,500)}Earphones and a Chorus of Cicadas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}They don't taste bad enough to throw away,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}but aren't good enough to call tasty, either
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}Downing cheap goods from the vending machine monopoly,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.01,0:01:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}today was the color of summer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.24,0:01:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}As the sunlight beat down,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}I dashed across the hot asphalt
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}Alone on a journey to a world unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}towards the world of summer I've longed for my whole life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}Not a single person in town 'cause of the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}I streamed a tune through my earphones
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}drowned out by the chorus of cicadas
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}and the sounds of summer carried on the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}Some sort of irritation nags at me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}and I can't throw out the negativity from yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}but the dew formed from anxiety and regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}is washed away by the evening showers in the world of summer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\an5\c&HFDFDFD&\pos(430,230)\fs30}A Summer Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:08.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}All I want is to live a summer dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,25)}Even after I get rid of all the emotions I don't need,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,25)}the unending cries are as loud as ever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:17.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(125,125)}"See, everything's okay here, no problem!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:19.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}I threw out my bluffs at pretending to be strong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(75,75)}Emptying on the inside, I made my presence transparent
